Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:03.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:06.87,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:09.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说时机已经成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:14.10,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但依旧缺少一个来主持仪式的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 我们也别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.64,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期满了 神的国近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:28.61,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quoniam impletum est tempus,et appropinquavit regnum Dei:poenitemini,et credite Evangelio





Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.92,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.61,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对亏你们两人的呼唤 我才能醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 幸村 千姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.55,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这打扰到你们感人的再会可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.83,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆彦大人 请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义仙已经开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:47.09,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们难道不应该联合起来对抗天草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:52.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个很不错的建议 柳生宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:56.85,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已经不需要借助你们的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经从那个十兵卫身上采集到了剑姬基因组
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.34,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑姬基因组
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.45,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然天然种就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.67,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们收集到了远超期望以上的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:14.12,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此终于得以一举实现一直停滞不前的伊邪那美计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.04,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊邪那美计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.16,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑姬基因组已经通过电脑网络传送完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:25.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快大江户的实验室就会公开量产型剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:32.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些最强少女们 能够在一小时内被送达至大日本的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.70,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经得到想要的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:39.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴? 我根本不需要那种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:48.57,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 那边的次品就当废物处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.63,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你听到没 没人要的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.74,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.91,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样还算是个将相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:56.94,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.62,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我德川庆彦可不是将相 是将军!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只要闭嘴乖乖服从我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.19,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.25,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 要是对我动手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.36,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的指挥系统可就要乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.15,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你当真要动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.15,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们不是还要说协助我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.73,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.78,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们互相打起来只会正中义仙下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:32.18,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没笨到回去和最强的剑姬打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.19,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.25,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好犹豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:38.99,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊十兵卫 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.03,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.31,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.46,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆彦大人 请快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.16,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.88,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论这个大日本会怎样你都不在乎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.52,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大日本? 管它去死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.60,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前妳肆意摆弄我的将相的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.22,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要好好回敬一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.85,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.34,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.51,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一介武士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.62,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白你是在对谁动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.46,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是将相 是将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.91,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢伤我将相之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.10,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是将军 我也照杀不误!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换模式 龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:43.96,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:45.91,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.82,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 得先去让十兵卫停手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.85,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神制御…原来还在起作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:01.60,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.46,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换模式 炎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.39,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 不光是速度快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.59,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.00,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.06,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.19,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.21,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 天然种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.60,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来妮雅更有优势嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.73,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.73,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么打下去 你的武士会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.50,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正现在我有数不尽的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.67,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是我的武士 就应该在这里光荣地牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你居然说出这么过分的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.10,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这男人到底要冷血到什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.66,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.87,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.21,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…她其实和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.31,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种将相…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.45,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么愚蠢的将相…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.65,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打从心底里爱慕着他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:27.21,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该没弱到因为那点程度的放热就动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.67,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在可以量产剑姬的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:35.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唯一能做的也就是尽量留下更多的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.04,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快点给我动手 妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:42.96,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 难道精神制御又坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.16,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.75,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底动不动 死废物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.34,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您难道还不明白吗 庆彦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:55.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的武士 根本不是收精神制御的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:59.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是她自愿为保护她的将相挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而哥哥你这种人 实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.76,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂武士心意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.25,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没资格率领剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.19,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实一群烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.89,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们这些天真的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑姬的数量才会不断减少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.88,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮雅 这是我最后的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.96,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不肯服从的话 你也给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:25.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还在为当年的关系介怀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bonjour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.75,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先自我介绍一下吧 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.58,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会长德川庆彦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.90,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有个从法兰西来的留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.69,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是超级大美人所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.54,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近我有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.21,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.49,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸鹤?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手很笨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.57,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是书写得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我瞧瞧 我来帮你叠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.55,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bonsoir
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.87,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳下山之后我们会这样问候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.16,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用诱骗其它学生一样的手法诱骗她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.65,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也调查到了她的基因信息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:37.76,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她那一眼识破我小丑般表演的洞察力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:46.16,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 她是第一个毫不畏惧学生会会长权势的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最值得我攻略的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那不过是场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 最后我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.53,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 注入剑姬基因组
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.03,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆彦 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:22.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮雅 你是第一个通过所有生物性测试的实验体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.11,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:31.60,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到一号人工剑姬居然是法国人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.72,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮雅 为了我 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.75,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大日本 助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:43.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆彦 求求你 快住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.65,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:52.78,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到发生了那种事还对我心存爱恋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:57.00,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮雅 去和下面得剑姬战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.12,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你到现在还没理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.99,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.70,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妳和将相一并斩杀才是武士慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.83,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 十兵卫 这场战斗根本没有正义可言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.72,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.41,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那个将相还在 这场战斗无法终结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.43,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗是注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:25.86,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪一边才是真正的正义 就来分个清白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上 妮雅 如果你真心爱我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残影闪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.77,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.59,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.41,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要胆敢拦我去路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:53.92,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人挡杀人 佛挡杀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:57.61,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了妮雅 你的爱就这点程度而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.20,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.70,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 快阻止她们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗是注定的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.15,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这世上有天之道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.94,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又岂能容许如此荒唐之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:21.18,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意这般珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.51,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以容人恣意践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.82,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.55,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 庆彦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.34,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆彦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.76,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信您是不那么糊涂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.09,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 净说这些废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.30,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能会明白我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.22,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看看您身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.53,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又着这么优秀的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:41.78,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 她是您身为优秀将相的最好证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.09,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀的将相? 无聊之极
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.88,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种玩意有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:56.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩负维持大日本和平和国民安宁重担的煎熬和压力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区百姓怎么能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.86,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为有你这种只知道空谈理想的家伙在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.83,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才导致大日本陷入这种危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:12.87,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quoniam impletum est tempus,et appropinquavit regnum Dei:poenitemini,et credite Evangelio
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 有一股灵力在不断剧增
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.13,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她开始行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村 千姬大人 你们从那边逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.70,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 我们在避难所会合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:44.85,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:49.42,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个研究所的设计应该能抵挡住10级的灵力冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.14,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳生义仙 你到底是怎么剧集到如此庞大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.19,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股震动…公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.90,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地震是怎么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.58,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村大人 您一定要平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱? 伙伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.51,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要管这些烦死人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.96,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁命令你来救我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.17,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.54,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.17,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是纸鹤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.15,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是全日本国民都是折纸的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:55.53,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:58.27,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头盔?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:02.95,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大日本的武士为保护将相而佩戴的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:06.92,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.97,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮雅真实个傻姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:15.51,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是送过你更多更好的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.82,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直把这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.11,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.00,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.86,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个优秀的将相?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.38,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是 怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.36,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.53,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能替你分担
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.05,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你独自一人肩负大日本的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.38,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.77,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天草四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.74,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.24,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天草四郎乃武士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.45,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我柳生义仙再次宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.93,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期满了 神的国近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:20.48,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当悔改 信福音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:25.69,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 日期满了 神的国近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.99,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当悔改 信福音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.56,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测到灵力的反常剧增
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:42.81,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳生义仙及天草四郎应该潜伏在茧中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.18,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空投全体剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.46,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:11.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.97,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 还没修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.02,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好 画面可以显示了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.66,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也算是剑姬吗 真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:33.46,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为将相庆彦不在 制约了她们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:38.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在唯一的希望就是德川庆彦的直属特殊部队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:42.15,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她们没了指挥官 不知能战到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.75,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 似乎敌人发现这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.91,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.39,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拼死一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:19:00.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算放下所有的防护墙 最多也只能撑到40分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.41,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村大人 十兵卫他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.91,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不在避难所里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.53,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 逃到避难所里的普通学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹他们也算是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.76,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不把她们叫来帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.95,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能帮得上忙早就叫来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.18,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实垃圾的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.58,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾是什么意思啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:32.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道妳有什么了不起的好主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.66,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.55,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 波动灵视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.64,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 醒醒 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.70,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.32,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗已经完全挣脱了锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.90,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:56.28,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他体内的将相之力已经完全觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:01.45,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个接吻 会成为宗朗和我真正的结契
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.62,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的结契…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:10.21,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 让我柳生十兵卫完全复活的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.52,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同时也意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:19.23,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于不完全结契而诞生的不完全的我会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.28,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不完全的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.37,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次和宗朗接吻的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:29.55,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人格就会从我的体内彻底消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:31.05,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.87,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.97,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 十兵卫 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.58,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:46.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.79,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼啊 南无阿弥陀佛 南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.10,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 妾身还没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.07,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我们来唤醒你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:00.40,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可就真的要死翘翘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.41,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这避难所也岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经容不得半刻犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.68,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须立刻逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.79,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:17.80,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:22.29,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个接吻 会成为真正的结契
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.35,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的结契
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.08,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人格会彻底消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:28.83,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.98,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:33.50,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百花缭乱 SAMURAI GIRLS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.26,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十一话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:39.86,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自法兰西的武士



Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.47,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事是由一个女孩从天而降开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:19.18,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的吻 将她们一个个变成了剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:21.34,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将相与武士的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.68,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼罩大日本的暗影 这些到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:27.03,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 我还是不知道如何解释它们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:29.67,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一点我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.01,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我现在应该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.99,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 出发吧 去迎接决战!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:35.74,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:37.61,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 百花缭乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.20,Default@HKG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诀别之吻

Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:36.16,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来?現在?束の間の愛は切なすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:40.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守られたい抱きしめたいどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:50.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ小さな花　風に打たれ　飛ばされないようにね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:56.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この身は永遠の旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last vision for last
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all day long　口ずさむ　単純な思いやり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:13.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,set me true　温もりを誰と分かつの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:18.16,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱された夢の秘密を返して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:23.06,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で流した涙の味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.96,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たい Raspberry mint
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:34.63,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひりひりと甘いよ…約束した筈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:40.10,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待って束の間の愛は切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:44.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守られたい抱きしめたいどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:54.75,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの綺麗な花　嵐の中散らされないようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.91,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震える声が消えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:36.16,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 現在 瞬間之愛 纏綿悱惻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:40.27,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何總是不斷渴求呵護與擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:50.83,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟願那嬌憐的花兒 不要在狂風中消殞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:56.01,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此身永為彷徨之旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.47,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last vision for last
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.27,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all day long 輕聲呢喃的單純關懷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:13.15,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,set me true 又可知這是誰的溫暖?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:18.16,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸還紛亂夢境中的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:23.06,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是淚水流過心底的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.96,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若冰冷的 Raspberry mint
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:34.63,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沁透肌膚的甘甜…早已與你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:40.10,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼即逝的瞬間 愛是難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:44.28,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何總是不斷渴求呵護與擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:54.75,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟願那絢麗的花兒 不要在暴風中凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.91,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的呼喊永無止息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.36,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（せっせ）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.85,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰の為でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽きない恋に招待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:57.22,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（恋はせっせ）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:02.53,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬉し恥ずかしゅうて今宵は好き放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（恋をせっせ）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力をください　あんあん安堵なんぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:10.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（どうよ？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:17.66,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これは切ない切りないギリギリ愛の詩…嗚呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:22.71,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口うつしの夢を飲んでね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:25.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（たぶんねきぶんで惚れるや）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:32.56,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとり長々しき夜に発熱したいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:34.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独壇場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:39.80,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独占は狩人の猛り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:39.92,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（きて　きて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:43.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つかまえて　つかまえて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:46.56,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲望が見たいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:48.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,また通りゃんせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:53.90,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一貫性求めても無駄よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:54.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（通せない）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:57.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋せっせ　よいよいよい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:22:59.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:22:59.97,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}（通して）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:04.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こころ籠の鳥じゃない　だっても取っ手もない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.07,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当に本当は嘘なの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:09.06,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御免！



